ShowForStonewall
================

Connect Stonewall with ShowFor to limit the display of attributes.
See http://github.com/bokmann/stonewall and http://github.com/plataformatec/show_for for details about each project.

http://github.com/saturnflyer/show_for_stonewall


Example
=======

Use it.


Requiremnts
===========

It currently assumes that you have current_user helper method in your controllers


